# Cursor Rules for StemPay Lottery Manager

## Auto-Update Rules
- **Contract Changes**: When `StemPayLotteryManager.sol` is modified, automatically check and update `RULES.md` and `StemPayLotteryManager.abi.json` to ensure they reflect the latest contract state

## Code Style
- **NO COMMENTS** except single descriptive comment on first line of contract files
- Write self-documenting code with clear, descriptive names
- Remove all inline, block, and documentation comments
- Use meaningful variable/function names instead of explanatory comments
